<html><head><meta charset="UTF-8"><link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="css/tips.css"></head><body><p><b>Version Control</b></p><p>IntelliJ IDEA provides out-of-the-box integration with the following version control systems: Git, Mercurial, Subversion, and Perforce.</p><p>Version your application to collaborate on it, as well as to eliminate the risks of storing all of your codebase locally. Press <span class="shortcut">&shortcut:ActivateVersionControlToolWindow;</span> to view the history of the changes in the project or press <span class="shortcut">&shortcut:CheckinProject;</span> to send your local changes to the repository.</p></body></html>